reviewText: Amazon needs to invent negative stars so that this book can receive an appropriate rating. The book is full of demonstrably false information. Science should literally sue Ken Ham for libel.
Wish I could give ZERO stars...people actually believe this stuff? WOW...get with the times.
Fast shipping, fantastic answers teen need to defend their faith in a fun, entertaining format!
Very thorough and clear! The explanations are very interesting!
